Package com.android.camera.gallery

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IImage
    The interface of all images used in gallery.
    IImageList
    The interface of all image collections used in gallery.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseImage
    Represents a particular image and provides access to the underlying bitmap and two thumbnail bitmaps as well as other information such as the id, and the path to the actual image data.
    BaseImageList
    A collection of BaseImages.
    Image
    The class for normal images in gallery.
    ImageList
    Represents an ordered collection of Image objects.
    ImageListUber
    A union of different IImageList.
    ImageListUber.AscendingComparator  
    ImageListUber.DescendingComparator  
    ImageListUber.MergeSlot
    A merging slot is used to trace the current position of a sublist.
    LruCache<K,V>  
    LruCache.Entry<K,V>  
    SingleImageList
    An implementation of interface IImageList which contains only one image.
    UriImage  
    VideoList
    A collection of all the VideoObject in gallery.
    VideoObject
    Represents a particular video and provides access to the underlying data and two thumbnail bitmaps as well as other information such as the id, and the path to the actual video data.
